R2AUD.original: ~z~I think I just persuaded them to drop your debt.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我刚才说服他们减轻了你的债务。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Niko, you're driving us to a hardware store on Dillon Street.
~z~That is why the ladies love me. Fuck those shylocks, they'll get their money.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~所以女人们才爱我。操他妈的讨债鬼，他们会拿到钱的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~All you people look same to me.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你们斯拉夫人长得都差不多。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Lose these cops, Niko. I don't want to lead them right to an illegal game.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~把条子甩了，Niko。我可不想把他们引进非法赌局。

R2AUD.original: ~z~See? Not everything I tell you was bullshit.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~看吧？我告诉你的东西也不全是胡扯。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You spoke then you say your phone out of batteries. You treat me like a bitch.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你一开口就是你手机没电了。你这是把我当婊子哪。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Cousin, you don't need to worry about those guys.
~z~Get rid of these cops, Niko. We can't lead them back to the depot.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~甩掉警察，Niko。我们不能把他们引到车行。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I do not understand it. I do everything I learn on TV.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我就不明白了，我明明是照电视上说的打的，

R2AUD.original: ~z~Maybe one day you get a premium quality one, like mine. Then you will have really made it.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~说不定哪天你也能用上高端手机，跟我这个一样。到时候你就是成功人士了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~In the old days we were dodging bombs, not loan sharks.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~以前我们躲的是轰炸，不是高利贷。

R2AUD.original: ~z~ In my homeland we have a saying...
~z~Funny. No! I'm the Janitor because I always clean up.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~真好笑。不！因为我总是横扫赌桌。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Roman, it looks like your money lending friends are here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~Roman，看样子借你钱的朋友们来了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Never! I'd treat you like an idiot, not a bitch, eh?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~没这回事！我把你当傻子，没把你当婊子，啊哈？

R2AUD.original: ~z~You just need know that I read book and I am very good at game.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你只要知道我读过书，还很擅长赌就行了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Niko, you have to lose these cops, we cannot lead them to my place of business.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，你得把条子甩了，别把他们引到我的车行去。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I really must win now. Leave me here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~现在我是不得不赢了。你先走吧。

R2AUD.original: ~z~~c~The Janitor. Sure.~s~ I seriously hope your cards are better than your nicknames.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~~c~清洁工。确实。~s~希望你的牌能比你的外号要好点。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Jesus, Roman, you fuckin' idiota. How can I take you seriously?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~天哪，Roman，你丫是白痴吧。这我怎么可能认真对你？

R2AUD.original: ~z~Do not hurt them, I know what you're like Niko Bellic.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~别伤着他们，我知道你是个什么人，Niko Bellic。

R2AUD.original: ~z~-I thought you were going to marry me, baby?~n~-Hey, Vlad.
~z~I see what I can do about getting money for cab.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我去想想怎么把买新车的钱弄来。

R2AUD.original: ~z~make them think you have the nuts in your hand.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~让他们认为你手里捏着炸弹。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Call me if some people show up in some shitty beige Willard. Those are the guys I owe money to.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~要是有几个人开着辆灰不拉几的Willard来了就打电话给我。我欠的就是他们的钱。

R2AUD.original: ~z~What have you done, cousin? This is not good. Others will come and take more money from us.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你都做了什么啊，堂弟？这可不好。会有别人找我们收更多钱的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Here are the loan sharks, of course.
~z~Because you can't pay your debts and they make you mop the floor?~c~ Incredible.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~因为你付不起账就让你拖地代偿？~c~不可思议。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Only problem is I'm playing with some money I'm meant to give to these Albanian scumbags.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~只不过我准备拿应该还那些阿尔巴尼亚混账的钱下注。

R2AUD.original: ~z~No, the business shut down a long time ago. We go there because some guys are playing cards.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~没有，五金店早就倒闭了。我们去是因为有人在那里打牌。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Come on, the piece of shit is gambling our money in here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~快点，那个人渣就在这里挥霍我们的钱。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I almost forgot. I'm giving you my old phone, my new number's in there.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~操，差点忘了。我的旧手机给你，我的新号已经存里面了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Remember, do not hurt the loan sharks. The debt will just increase.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~记住，不要伤着讨债的，否则债上加债。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You should lose few pounds - otherwise this beautiful lady is going to leave you.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你也该减减肥了，不然这位美丽的女士可就要离你而去了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Another piece of shit, straight off the boat.
~z~Here's hoping they don't show up, eh?
~z~- there is a lot of stuff I must get used to here in Liberty City.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~在自由城我还有很多东西要去适应。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Baby... when I look into your eyes, it means something.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~宝贝...当我望向你的眼中时，是有一些含义的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I am the best. I kick all the asses that play me. They call me the Janitor.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我最强。跟我赌的那群混账都没有好下场。他们管我叫清洁工。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Why are we going to this hardware store? You need to buy something?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~去五金店干嘛？你有什么东西要买吗？

R2AUD.original: ~z~And this must be the loan sharks.
~z~Very difficult, I think... hello, Roman! Hello, Miss...
R2AUD.translated: ~z~很困难，我想...你好啊，Roman！你好，这位...

R2AUD.original: ~z~Here in Liberty City, we speak English. Get used to this.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~这里是自由城，我们都讲英文。赶紧适应吧。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I know... I'm a fat prick, what can I do?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我知道...我就一肥猪，我能怎么办？

R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, this is fucked. Now I going to be in even more debt.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，这下坏事了。现在我是要债上加债了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Please don't hurt the men after us, cousin. They hate me enough as it is.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~拜托别伤着追我们的人，堂弟。他们已经够恨我了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~We got loan sharks after us?~c~ Roman? What's going on?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~有讨债的追着我们？~c~Roman？怎么回事？

R2AUD.original: ~z~I hope you're less full of shit than your cousin over here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~希望你这人没你堂兄那么扯。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Just drive. Leave the funny comments to me.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~专心开车吧。耍嘴皮子的事我来。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You and your debts, Roman. ~c~Always the same. Never change.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你和一屁股债，Roman。~c~到哪都一样。从未变过。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, Niko, it's them, they must have been told I was here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~妈的，Niko，就是他们，肯定是有人告诉他们我在这了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You can play, right? ~c~You are good at this game?
~z~~c~It don't make no sense to me neither.
~z~Do not hurt them, I know what you're like, Niko Bellic.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~别伤着他们，我知道你是个什么人，Niko Bellic。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You're taking me to a backroom game where I'll win all the dollars we need to really see this town.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你开车送我去地下赌场，我在那就能把需要的钱都赢来，带你在城里好好见识见识。

R2AUD.original: ~z~It's about making other players think you have best cards,
R2AUD.translated: ~z~写的是让对手认为你有最好的手牌，

R2AUD.original: ~z~The money, the people, all of this noise around us
~z~After me, and it doesn't matter anyway.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~是追我。其实也没什么大不了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I think that Bellic is in this store. We will get our money.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我想那个Bellic就在这家店里。我们会收到账的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Now they take all my money from me.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~现在他们把我的钱都拿走了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~What you doing? Now we going to be in real trouble.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你做了啥啊？现在我们是真有麻烦了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~When I've played this game I'll have enough money to pay them back ten times.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~等我赌完，我就会有足够还他们十次的钱。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Call me if some Albanians show up in some shitty beige Willard. Those are the guys I owe money to.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~要是有几个阿尔巴尼亚人开着灰不拉几的Willard来了就打电话给我。我欠的就是他们的钱。

R2AUD.original: ~z~No, funny guy - we going to get money. In America you need money to do anything.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~不，真会说笑...我们去挣钱。在美国，做什么事都要钱。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Cousin, shit. Why you no warn me that these guys are coming in the store?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~堂弟，操。你怎么不告诉我这群人已经进店了？

R2AUD.original: ~z~Yes, he's all charm. Come on Niko, let's go.
~z~I see little Romans, I see little Mallories,
~z~They're gone, perfect. That is the last we have seen of those loan sharks... I hope.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~他们走了，很好。希望这是我们最后一次遇上那些讨债的...

R2AUD.original: ~z~~c~I will believe when I see, Roman.
~z~Alright cousin, I'll lose them.~c~ Not so tough now.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~好了堂兄，我会甩掉他们的。~c~这可不难。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Quick, you take us back to the cab depot. That is Dardan.
~z~No, no, this is my game that they play.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~不，不是的，这次是在我的局里玩他们。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You think anyone will let me take out insurance policy? We see.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你说保险公司肯不肯赔？试试吧。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Doing some home improvements, Roman? You going to build this mansion you tell me about?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~要搞住房改造吗，Roman？你是想自己造一个跟我说过的豪宅？

R2AUD.original: ~z~I raise on flop, I ride river, it don't make no sense.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我逆风加注，逆流而上，怎么就不管用呢。

R2AUD.original: ~z~If you have their nuts in your hand, I believe they will know about it anyway.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~要是你手里捏着他们的蛋，他们肯定会知道吧。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Get us back to the depot, quick!
~z~~c~Has always been that way with you, Roman.
~z~I think that speaking this language should be the least of my problems.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~说英文应该是最容易适应的部分。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Don't worry I'm getting so many bullets it's like I'm an AK. ~c~We're cool.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~别担心，我手头弹药充足，感觉自己像把AK。~c~没问题的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Everything that I read in the books. I do what Car Jabowitz tell me in 'May Contain Nuts.'
R2AUD.translated: ~z~明明照着书里写的打了。我照着Car Jabowitz写的《可能有弹》来的。
~z~我看见了群星，我看见了天使。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I have the feeling only thing you will come out of there with is more debt.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我有预感，打完牌出来你只会背上更多的债。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Maybe a few more after this game you just lose.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~今天输完钱估计还得多几个。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Sure. I will remind you of that in a few weeks.
~z~You cannot run from us forever, Mr. Roman.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你躲得了一时躲不了一世，Roman先生。

R2AUD.original: ~z~tell this fucking yokel here if he doesn't stop staring at me,
R2AUD.translated: ~z~告诉这个傻逼乡巴佬，他要是再盯着我，

R2AUD.original: ~z~It's all quiet out here Roman, you winning? ~c~Please say yes.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~外面很平静，Roman，手气好吗？~c~希望你手气不错。

R2AUD.original: ~z~-Hi.~n~-Niko, this is Mallorie, the beautiful girl I tell you about...
R2AUD.translated: ~z~－嗨。~n~－Niko，这位是Mallorie，我跟你说过的美女...

R2AUD.original: ~z~Hey, they have stopped following us. Clearly they are too scared of what I could do to them.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~喂，他们没再追过来了。肯定是怕我对他们做些什么。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Sorry, I forget, there are many of these men you owe money to.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~抱歉，我忘了。你的债主都长得差不多。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Niko, you're new. You don't understand the way things work.
~z~I'm going to take them for everything they have.
~z~Shit, I have to call these loan sharks and try to make things cool.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~操，我得打电话给这些高利贷求情了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Cousin - two guys are going in the store. I think they are the loan sharks you speak of.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~堂兄，两个人要进店了。他们应该就是你说的讨债的。

R2AUD.original: ~z~I'll have his head chopped off and put a film of it on the internet!
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我就把他的头砍下来拍成录像上传上网！

R2AUD.original: ~z~Mallorie, this is my cousin I tell you about, Niko...
R2AUD.translated: ~z~Mallorie，这个就是我跟你说过的堂弟，Niko...

R2AUD.original: ~z~Roman Bellic, we will find you soon.
~z~I lost it this time, but when I go back the last thing they will expect is for me to take everything.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~这次我是输光了，但下次再来的时候，他们一定想不到我会赢走一切。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Niko, wait for me here while I go inside to clean up.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~Niko，我进去横扫的时候你就在这等我。

R2AUD.original: ~z~That is his cab, the fat Roman must be in here.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~他的出租在这，Roman这胖子肯定在这里。

R2AUD.original: ~z~It is the Russian mobsters, Vlad's bosses, that run everything. Be careful of them.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~俄罗斯黑帮，Vlad的上级才是掌控全局的人。不要招惹他们。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Anyway, I read this book, 'May Contain Nuts.'
R2AUD.translated: ~z~总之，我读了他的书，《或许有弹》。

R2AUD.original: ~z~the beautiful women do like the guys with the funny sense of humor.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~漂亮女人确实都喜欢幽默男人。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Darling... I'll see you later. I've got to take my cousin around some more, get him settled...
R2AUD.translated: ~z~亲爱的...我们待会儿见。我还得带我堂弟出去多转两圈，帮他适应适应...

R2AUD.original: ~z~Come on, big guy - either do some work or get out of here. We don't need jokers.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~拜托，大哥，要么干活，要么滚蛋。我们不养闲人。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Of course they saw you. I mean... you're a distinctive man Roman.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~肯定看见你了。我是说...你这人很显眼，Roman。

R2AUD.original: ~z~He on TV whole time. The Buffet Car? Come on.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~他天天上电视的。人送外号餐饮列车？拜托。

R2AUD.original: ~z~You and your debts, Roman. ~c~Always the same. Never change.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你和一屁股债，Roman。~c~到哪都一样。从未变过。

R2AUD.original: ~z~-Thank you.~n~-This is the woman that I'm going to marry!
R2AUD.translated: ~z~－谢谢夸奖。~n~－这就是我要娶的女人！

R2AUD.original: ~z~You tell me to behave, Mr. Janitor? If you understand it all, where is the money?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~你还能教我规矩，清洁工先生？你要是啥都明白，那钱到哪儿去了？

R2AUD.original: ~z~You are a friend of the fat Roman?
~z~We're at the bottom of the ladder man. These thugs push us around. But they are not to be feared.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我们在底层，老弟。这些恶棍肆意压迫我们，但他们不算什么。

R2AUD.original: ~z~And I'm going to win lot of money for us.
~z~I... I will do man. We spoke of this.
~z~Shit, you ain't going to make sense to no people if you keep speaking in that language.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~操，再说这种鸟语，就没人能听懂你说的话了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~We should stand up to them.~c~ Where is your pride?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我们应该反抗他们。~c~你的尊严呢？

R2AUD.original: ~z~I have read all the books. You know Car Jabowitz?
R2AUD.translated: ~z~我可是读过书的。认识Car Jabowitz吗？

R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, cousin. We can't lead these cops right to this backroom game. Lose them.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~操，堂弟。我们不能把这群条子引到地下赌局去。甩掉他们。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, we got one too. You're a fag!
R2AUD.translated: ~z~对，我们那儿也有一句。你个基佬！

R2AUD.original: ~z~Shit, I almost forgot. I'm giving you my old phone, my new number's in there.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~操，差点忘了。我的旧手机给你，我的新号已经存里面了。

R2AUD.original: ~z~If they had not taken it, other players would have. It's all the same, Roman.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~就算他们没拿，也会被别人赢走的。都一样的，Roman。

R2AUD.original: ~z~Look, say what you like,but at least that guy knows how to speak to a lady.
R2AUD.translated: ~z~听着，随你怎么说吧，但至少人家知道怎么跟女士说话。
